    • Fibonacci
    def fib_memo(n, cache):
    # ì½”ë“œë¥¼ ì‘ì„±í•˜ì„¸ìš”.
    if n < 3:
        return 1
    else:
        if n in cache:
            return cache[n]
        else:
            cache[n] = fib_memo(n-1, cache) + fib_memo(n-2, cache)
            return cache[n]
